snippet.title: Jelly Escape Preview Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the preview trailer for the upcoming funny-tricky-platformer-retro-80's-arcade TawStudio's new title: Jelly Escape!

Can you manage to escape over 60 chambers of imprisoning laboratories, while unlocking several other jellies, chambers, and bonus contents?

Stay tuned for news and updates through our channels:
Twitter: twitter.com/TawStudio
Facebook: facebook.com/TawStudio
